Cactus Code Thorn DriftCorrect4
Thorn Author(s)     : Erik Schnetter <schnetter@aei.mpg.de>
Thorn Maintainer(s) : Erik Schnetter <schnetter@aei.mpg.de>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:

Lock an apparent horizon to a fixed coordinate position, using
rotational and radial corrections.
